            <me>
            \text{span}\left(\begin{bmatrix}5\\0\\4\end{bmatrix}, \begin{bmatrix}0\\4\\2\end{bmatrix}\right).
        </me>
       </p>
    </statement>
    <answer>
        <p>
            First, observe that <m>[5,0,4], [0,4,2]</m> are not scalar multiples of each other.  
        </p>

<image width="80%">
